description: "The residency of Soerabaja, East Java, featuring crops (coffee, coconut, sugarcane, rice, alang-alang, bamboo) and fishing ponds. Three inset maps: a triangulation map; a map of distances between settlements by types of transport; Bawean Island."
title: "A new chart of the straits of Sunda. : From the manuscript of the Dutch East India Company corrected and improved by Captn. Henry Smedley of the Raymond 1785, Captn. Parker of the Bridgewater 1787, and of Captn. John Hall, of the Worcester, 1788 &c.. [cartographic material]"
